  {"id":"class_question","name":"举起手","ageMin":7,"ageMax":12,"weight":3,"text":"老师提出了一个没人回答的问题。你知道答案，要举手吗？","choices":[{"text":"举起手，说出答案","condition":{"attribute":"intelligence","op":"gte","value":5},"requirementText":"智力达到 5","resultText":"答案是对的。掌声很轻，却让你记了很久。","result":{"attributes":{"intelligence":1,"charm":1},"addTags":["课堂自信"]}},{"text":"再想一想，保持沉默","resultText":"另一个人回答了。你在本子上认真写下完整过程。","result":{"attributes":{"intelligence":1}}}],"repeatable":false},
